s dressed in head-to-toe Saint Laurent. (She also attended Vaccarello=E2=80=
=99s Legion of Honor ceremony this evening.) At one point, Vaccarello was v=
iewed as a potential successor for Versace. But that<em>
actually</em> was a long time ago.</li></ul></div>
