hat pairing suggests that La Beaut=C3=A9 isn=E2=80=99t going for mass appea=
l=E2=80=A6 at least at first. Instead, expect super luxe ingredients and ex=
travagant packaging (I heard lipsticks will retail for around $80 to $90), =
with limited
distribution. High-fashion beauty, in other words=E2=80=94a nice little add=
-on when someone buys a handbag, or a consolation prize, perhaps, for peopl=
e who spent half an hour in line just to ogle a $3,000 bag.</p></div>
